actions.text: Referred to House Committee on Agriculture.

official_title: A bill to authorize the Secretary of Agriculture to convey certain real property located within the Nicolet National Forest, Wisc., to certain communities for use as solid waste disposal sites.

summary.text: Authorizes the Secretary of Agriculture to convey specified real property located within the Nicolet National Forest, Wisconsin, to local communities for use as solid waste disposal sites.

titles.title: A bill to authorize the Secretary of Agriculture to convey certain real property located within the Nicolet National Forest, Wisc., to certain communities for use as solid waste disposal sites.
